"ShanexRosalieTheWinterMM.18": "@, I need you to give me your honest opinion...$2 #$b# You've been around with me through a lot of my hard moments. #$b# I don't trust very easily... But I know you're not just a nice person.$2 #$b# You're also good. If it weren't for you, I don't know if Shane and I would be together now. #$b# And... well...$6",
