"ShanexRosalieTheWinterMM.21": "It's not becuase I want to!$6 #$b# It's just...$2 #$b# I sent in a tape for an audition. I didn't think anything of it. #$b# The part was for someone who... doesn't typically look like me....$2 #$b# But apparently the casting director recognized my voice on The Voice of the Valley...$8 #$b# and I got the gig...$1",
"ShanexRosalieTheWinterMM.22": "It's an amazing opportunity. It's a dream come true.$1 #$b# But... I'd be gone for a whole season... Every year.$2 #$b# I know it sounds extreme to break up with Shane, but... I've been held back and kept from my dream so many times before him.$2 #$b# I never want to be put through that again... I won't... No matter what.$3 #$b# But I'm scared that he'll put me in that position where I need to break things off with him.$11",
