"ShanexRosalieTheWinterMM.40": "You know that if the roles were reversed, if I had the opportunity to play gridball again, you'd be packing my bags for me.$6 #$b# Hell, we spent the first four years of our friendship making sure that happened.$1 #$b# Now, it's my turn now to support you.$6 #$b# And yeah, I'm gonna miss you like crazy, but what's one season to twenty years apart?$1 #$b# And if it ever becomes too much, you know I'll be right here waiting for you.$4 #$b# I'm not in such a dark place anymore, Rosa. You and @ helped me with that.$4",
